Ancient Cedar Circle~
Massive cedar trunks ring this quiet clearing in an almost perfect circle, their roots spreading wide. @@GTheir combined canopy muffles trail sounds and dims the midday light to a soft green.@@N Bark from the oldest cedar has cracked into deep orange furrows over centuries of growth.

