Mossy Overlook~
A moss-covered rise lifts the path above the lower trail corridors and wetland edges below. @@GFrom this vantage, both the creek and the cedar grove are visible through gaps in the canopy.@@N A flat stone here serves as an informal rest seat for tired visitors who pause on the climb.

