Pine Needle Run~
Soft pine needles carpet this side trail underfoot, muffling every footstep completely. @@GYoung pines and cedar saplings crowd close on either side, their branches brushing the path.@@N The needles release a clean resinous scent when crushed underfoot. Light filters @@Ggreen@@N through the dense young canopy above.

